plot: The Catanias go out for a celebratory family dinner, Paul and Brittany included. Frank continues to poke at Paul as Paul hints there may be more than just one wedding in the group's near future. Rachel and John share big news with Jaiden. Danielle and her mom attempt to move on from the pain Danielle's brother has caused the family. Still feeling the luck of the Irish, Paul and Dolores plan a fun, Prohibition-themed party. However, while getting ready for the party, Louie surprises Teresa when he lets loose about how he really feels about her brother.—Anonymous
